avors of executive chef Danny Ibarra, who marries the traditions and history of South Texas with the finesse of the world's finest restaurants. Whether you enjoy your experience nestled among the limestone walls inside the restaurant, at a table along the riverwalk or on a barge while floating on the river itself, you'll see how Boudro's transforms a meal into a dining event. For any occasion, from romantic dinners to power meetings we offer it all.", photoCount: "1203.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 107, \"count2\": 150, \"count3\": 493, \"count4\": 1321, \"count5\": 2886}", email: "restaurant@boudros.com", website: "http://boudros.com", rankingPosition: "17.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1320, \"closeHours\": \"22:00\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1350, \"closeHours\": \"22:30\"}], [{\"open\": 660, \"openHours\": \"11:00\", \"close\": 1350, \"closeHours\": \"22:30\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Chicago\"}", address: "421 E Commerce St, San Antonio, TX 78205-2814", neighborhoodLocations: "[{\"id\": \"21002007\", \"name\": \"Downtown\"}]", dishes: ["Crab", "Crab Cake", "Filet Mignon", "Burger", "Lobster", "Oyster", "Polenta", "Pork Tenderloin", "Ribs", "Shrimp", "Surf And Turf", "Tapas", "Tortillas", "Salad", "Shrimp and Grits", "Bread Pudding", "Scallops", "Salmon", "Tuna", "Quail", "Seafood Platters", "Beef", "Duck", "Shellfish", "Cakes", "Fish", "Pork", "Enchiladas", "Lobster Tail", "Soup", "Coconut Shrimp", "Flan", "Fish Platter", "Tostadas", "Tostada", "Mole", "Puddings", "Cake", "Prickly Pear Margarita", "Guacamole", "Fried"], re